name: Global Catastrophe: I Begin to Evolve from an Ancient Tree
summary: Reborn as an Ancient Tree, Gu Qingyang activates the data panel, allowing him to evolve and break through as long as he devours living beings.Gu Qingyang has kept a low profile and cultivated for ten years until blood rains from the sky.......“Those who believe in me shall have eternal life!”
author: The sun and the moon share the sky.
